docker.io-app (29.1.3-0ubuntu4) resolute; urgency=medium

  The docker.io package now ships the following files:

  * /usr/share/docker.io/contrib/dockerd-rootless-setuptool.sh
  * /usr/share/docker.io/contrib/dockerd-rootless.sh

  These are helper scripts which can be optionally used to run the docker
  daemon and containers as a non-root user. See
  https://docs.docker.com/engine/security/rootless/ for further reference.

 -- Athos Ribeiro <athos@ubuntu.com>  Tue, 31 Mar 2026 11:19:09 -0300
